name: HomelessCat DAO
description: Our goal is bringing global homeless cats to Satoshi Island. Where will be a heaven of crypto lover, freedome pursuer, and no more abandonment. Kittens have a home and be loved, we will generate a collectable NFT of the homeless cats that be rescued, distribute them to donators. And try to get a piece of land in Sandbox to build the HLCD paradise. Let the poors cats not only have home in their life, also in the metaverse.
